videos.headline: Taylor lunges for the goal line scoring the TD
videos.description: Heisman hopeful Jonathan Taylor scores the touchdown after it was originally ruled he was down, putting Wisconsin up 13-3.

videos.headline: Nebraska WR hurdles defender
videos.description: Nebraska wide receiver Stanley Morgan Jr. goes airborn and clears the Wisconsin defender.

videos.headline: Wisconsin TE goes high up in the air for the TD catch
videos.description: Wisconsin tight end Jake Ferguson leaps and makes the touchdown catch to extend the Badgers' lead to 20-3.

videos.headline: Nebraska WR takes off for a 75-yard TD
videos.description: Nebraska wide receiver JD Spielman catches the pass then breezes to the end zone for the 75-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Taylor scores 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor follows his blocks and runs into the end zone putting the Badgers up 27-10.

videos.headline: Nebraska's Morgan leaps over defender
videos.description: Cornhuskers wideout Stanley Morgan Jr. plants his feet and hurdles over a would-be tackler to pick up the first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nebraska’s Morgan leaps over defender) 2018/10/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin RB stiff-arms his way into the enc zone for the TD
videos.description: Wisconsin running back Taiwan Deal breaks free and stiff-arms a defender for the 20-yard touchdown run.
